title: Celebrity Big Brother voting figures reveal Coleen Nolan triumphed over Jedward with a narrow lead of just three per cent as tight race went down to the wire
text:
TV Magazine Two Horse Race Celebrity Big Brother voting figures reveal Coleen Nolan triumphed over Jedward with a narrow lead of just three per cent as tight race went down to the wire 
The other contestants didn't even come near to the top two as the full numbers were revealed by show bosses Revealed
